  "description": {
    "short": "Internal sandbox build of the Alfred meeting assistant",
    "full": "Internal sandbox build of the Alfred meeting assistant. Joins Teams meetings, captures real-time diarized audio, reads and writes meeting chat, and surfaces live notes and summaries in an external workspace. All access is granted per-chat at install time via resource-specific consent (RSC); no tenant-wide Microsoft Graph permissions are required."
  },
